title: Lubricated Goat Discography
description:
Lubricated Goat is an experimental rock/post-punk musical project headed by composer Stuart Gray (Stu Spasm). Mainly influenced by bands like The Stooges and The Birthday Party, they are credited for playing a grimy, confrontational style of rock which preceded grunge.

contains:
(1987) Plays the Devil's Music
(1988) Paddock of Love
(1989) Schadenfreude
(1990) Psychedelicatessen
(1993) Crunt: Crunt
(1994) Forces You Don't Understand
(2003) The Great Old Ones

genre: Noise Rock, Post-Punk
format: v0 mp3
